{
  "stem": "27507.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to him-- I couldn't get the words out, I was so shocked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said Papa, Tata in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Papa, your hair is burning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his hair caught fire from the carbide lamp, and was completely burned, burned altogether.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it grew again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- so carbide lamps were not safe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "January '43, yes, and I remember of this period-- well, I remember all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember Germans coming, and the groups of maybe army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it was army or SS, coming, and singing their songs, marching through the ghetto, and singing those songs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember houses burning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They already then were burning groups of houses, of those wild houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it was just a fire that started and got out of control.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was this tremendous, tremendous fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And January came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in January, there was another action.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in January, that action was in mid-January, maybe 15th of January.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the Jews didn't appear anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They hid in the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't come out to be taken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't allow themselves to be taken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the action was-- and we hid in a bunker as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We hid in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In Nowolipki, there was a bunker, which was-- somehow, there was a dentist surgery somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And under the dentist's chair, they made an entrance to the bunker-- or behind the dentist's chair, next to the dentist's chair-- there was an entrance which was well-masked this time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was, this time, a professional job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a bunker, quite a big bunker with many people there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we hid there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was pretty unsuccessful, that action.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
